Questions Q1 - Q2

 test_data %>% 
  select(OMID, Q1Pre, Q2Pre, Q1Post, Q2Post, Q1FollowUp, Q2FollowUp) %>% 
  gather(key, value, -OMID) %>% 
  mutate(value = ifelse(str_detect(value, "asked") | nchar(value) == 0, NA, as.numeric(value))) %>% 
  # filter(value > 100)
  ggplot(aes(value, color = key)) +
  geom_density() +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 0) +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 100)  +
  openmindR::theme_om()  +
  openmindR::scale_color_om() +
  theme(legend.position = "right")

test_data %>% 
  select(OMID, Q1Pre, Q2Pre, Q1Post, Q2Post, Q1FollowUp, Q2FollowUp) %>% 
  gather(key, value, -OMID) %>% 
  mutate(value = ifelse(str_detect(value, "asked") | nchar(value) == 0, NA, as.numeric(value))) %>%
  drop_na(value) %>% 
  assertr::verify(value >= 0)%>% 
  assertr::verify(value <= 100)

Question S1

Is S1 always asked? Because some are missing.

test_data %>% 
  select(OMID, S1Pre, S1Post, S1FollowUp) %>% 
  gather(key, value, -OMID) %>% 
  mutate(value = ifelse(str_detect(value, "asked") | nchar(value) == 0, NA, value)) %>% 
  count(key, value) %>% 
  mutate(value = str_remove_all(value, "abortion rights, Black Lives Matter, gun control")) %>% 
  drop_na(value) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(value, n)) +
    geom_col(aes(fill = key), position = position_dodge()) + 
  coord_flip()  +
  openmindR::theme_om()  +
  openmindR::scale_fill_om() +
  theme(legend.position = "right")
